36
00:01:26,230 --> 00:01:28,570
In addition, other
students frequently

37
00:01:28,570 --> 00:01:31,300
jump in with great
advice and answers

38
00:01:31,300 --> 00:01:32,980
if you get stuck on a lab.

39
00:01:32,980 --> 00:01:34,240
We're almost ready to begin.

